### Definir WEBHOOK por instância (use seu token da instância)
POST https://hia-clientes.uazapi.com/webhook
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
token: {{UAZAPI_TOKEN}}

{
  "url": "https://leandro-sem-n8n-production.up.railway.app/webhook/Leandro-JW"
}

### (Alternativa) Se a API esperar 'webhook' ao invés de 'url'
POST https://hia-clientes.uazapi.com/webhook
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
token: {{UAZAPI_TOKEN}}

{
  "webhook": "https://leandro-sem-n8n-production.up.railway.app/webhook/Leandro-JW"
}

### Ver WEBHOOK por instância
GET https://hia-clientes.uazapi.com/webhook
Accept: application/json
token: {{UAZAPI_TOKEN}}

### (Opcional) Definir WEBHOOK GLOBAL (exige admin token)
POST https://hia-clientes.uazapi.com/globalwebhook
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
adminToken: {{UAZAPI_ADMIN_TOKEN}}

{
  "url": "https://leandro-sem-n8n-production.up.railway.app/webhook/Leandro-JW"
}

### (Opcional) Ver WEBHOOK GLOBAL
GET https://hia-clientes.uazapi.com/globalwebhook
Accept: application/json
adminToken: {{UAZAPI_ADMIN_TOKEN}}